{{External|rs=Emir Shah}}
The '''Emir''' is the ruler of [[Al Kharid]], a small city on the northern fringe of the massive [[Kharidian Desert]]. Since his [[Prince Ali|son]]'s kidnapping, the Emir has been in no state to directly govern Al Kharid, and he has retreated to his private chambers where only [[Hassan]], the Chancellor, may see him. He has ruled the desert town for many years, and it is his only wish that his son, [[Prince Ali]], might be raised to run the state with the same good hand.{{CiteGeneral|url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090522043551/http://www.runescape.com/kbase/viewarticle.ws?article_id=2648|title=''RuneScape'' website - Game Guide - Area Guides - Cities and Towns - Al Kharid}}

